-- Sharapova Defeats Kvitova to Advance to First French Open Final
-- B y   B o b   B e n s c h
-- 2012-06-07T17:11:28Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-06-07/sharapova-defeats-kvitova-to-advance-to-first-french-open-final.html
Maria Sharapova  beat Wimbledon
champion Petra Kvitova 6-3, 6-3 to advance to her first French
Open final.  Sharapova will play Sara Errani, who beat Samantha Stosur
7-5, 1-6, 6-3, for the title at Roland Garros in Paris. The
Russian is seeking to complete the career Grand Slam after
previously winning the Australian Open, Wimbledon and U.S. Open.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Bob Bensch at 
 bbensch@bloomberg.net  